{"tid":2042490,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（冇5毛post）夠喇！根本唔係咩蝴蝶效應 係有人一直小事化大","createTime":"2020-05-30T00:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T02:12:49.000Z","uid":84081,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16344a55347ae1fd6194c86a47746b8ddd441c6b","tid":2042490,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:43:01.000Z","msg":"成日話咩陳同佳綠帽搞到世界大戰<br />\n<br />\n大家睇返以前「尖閣諸島國有化事件」<br />\n<br />\n689唔跟貪曾慣例 畀保釣船出海<br />\n搞到日本將尖閣諸島收歸國有<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候某人係管理稀土出口<br />\n佢大刀闊斧停止供應稀土 官方罕有地容許反日示威<br />\n國際好快就自己搵稀土 解決咗件事<br />\n<br />\n當時已經睇得出呢個人係唔識大事化小<br />\n處事下下都強硬<br />\n<br />\n畀佢上位之後<br />\n一戴一露<br />\n亞投行<br />\n中國製造2025<br />\n東莞收皮<br />\n有邊樣係掂？"},{"pid":"9ccdf228089ee58bf505ec6366d642b2b9bc952e","tid":2042490,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:44:28.000Z","msg":"最成功咪閱兵既藍天計劃囉<br />\n唔畀廠開工一個月就整個藍天白雲出黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11835e52411dcd1c697f3275b47dad92110662d","tid":2042490,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:45:19.000Z","msg":"文學修養最掂 - 此句不唸"},{"pid":"bb391c6cf65797f92f7957bee8dfe81a59d88ad0","tid":2042490,"uid":84081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:46:58.000Z","msg":"成日都陳同佳陳同佳<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳呢單野畀貪曾搞根本唔會上到國際新聞<br />\n一拉人就掉去台灣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係有人想借機搞事<br />\n <br />\n但佢又唔知上邊鐘意小事化大<br />\n好小事都要搞到國際關係崩潰"},{"pid":"ea8386f5c6652b93305f89b3d05726b333cb6090","tid":2042490,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:48:59.000Z","msg":"個綠帽gag 都搞到悶啦"},{"pid":"f982e25b1d08891871809bf6f77524b05d3ffb41","tid":2042490,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f11835e52411dcd1c697f3275b47dad92110662d","tid":2042490,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:45:19.000Z","msg":"文學修養最掂 - 此句不唸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:50:34.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n有郭安發大家心照不宣啦<br />\n<br />\n根本係大粒乜都唔識<br />\n道家思想係治國如煮小鮮 <br />\n慢慢黎 由小事著手 一步步改善大家生活<br />\n<br />\n我靜係知豬肉因為進口俄佬肉搞到貴曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係邊個既主意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fd5d8077f38efce94cc86d28f7bc5a0820f50f","tid":2042490,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:55:13.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n真係冇5毛<br />\n幾撚易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df4b927f0293bc4f8458ba3805925d348185804","tid":2042490,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6fd5d8077f38efce94cc86d28f7bc5a0820f50f","tid":2042490,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:55:13.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n真係冇5毛<br />\n幾撚易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:09:42.000Z","msg":"無人推你po sosad"},{"pid":"68aa92990edd043f77ceb7c97981585acadb8afa","tid":2042490,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"推"}]}